sentences: Nikolai Hængsle (previously Nikolai Hængsle Eilertsen; born 24 June 1978)
He is primarily known as a member of BigBang (1999–2004, 2009–present) and The National Bank (2004–present).
Eilertsen, who was born in Skotselv, also participates in the bands Lester, Needlepoint and Elephant9.
